info.name: aaveFlashLoan
info.description: 1st Place  in the Gitcoin Web3 World Aave Hackathon. A bot that does arbitrage between two Uniswap exchanges using an Aave Flashloan as the capital for initial trade. Got a nice write up from the Aave team - https://medium.com/aave/gitcoin-x-aave-hackathon-recap-f61d24af2cb
